value.name: Super Friends: The Legendary Super Powers Show
value.original_name: Super Friends: The Legendary Super Powers Show
value.overview: Super Friends: The Legendary Super Powers Show is an American animated television series about a team of superheroes which ran from 1984 to 1985 on ABC. It was produced by Hanna-Barbera and is based on the Justice League and associated comic book characters published by DC Comics.
